# Light Sensor

> [!word] Light Sensor
>
> Light [[61-Archive/20220311115526-sensors|sensors]] are photo-electric device that converts **light energy** (_photons_) detected to **[[61-Archive/20220408132112-electrical-energy|electrical energy]]** (_[[61-Archive/20220408114349-electron|electrons]]_).

- Examples

  - [[61-Archive/20220311121856-photo-resistor|light-dependent resistor]]
  - Photo-diode
  - Photo-transistor
